---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Join EduMyna - Team & Partner Deck"
  description="The 12-year journey to EduMyna. How building 500 startups, partnering with tech giants, and teaching thousands of students led to one clear mission."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-blue-900 to-slate-900 text-white">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-4xl py-20 md:py-32">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-blue-300 mb-6">Team & Partner Recruitment</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight mb-6">
          The 12-Year Journey to EduMyna
        </h1>
        <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-slate-300 font-light mb-8">
          How building 500 startups, partnering with tech giants, and teaching thousands of students led to one clear mission
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-400">— Gautam, Founder</p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <Container>
    <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 md:py-24 space-y-24">

      <!-- Where It Started -->
      <section id="where-it-started">
        <div class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">2009</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Where It Started</h2>

        <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-6">"What if Kerala could be India's Silicon Coast?"</p>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-600 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">The Vision (2009)</p>
          <p class="text-blue-800 mb-4">MobME proposed India's first Public-Private-Partnership incubator. Enable entrepreneurs. Build a startup ecosystem from scratch.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-700"><strong>The Commitment:</strong> 10,000 sq ft space, ₹2.5 crore grant, support 48 startups over five years</p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">What Actually Happened</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-green-500 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600">500</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Startups Supported</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">10x the commitment</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-green-500 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600">3,139</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Jobs Created</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-green-500 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600">₹45Cr</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Raised by Alumni</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-xl p-6">
          <p class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">ROI: ₹9.68 for every ₹1 government investment</p>
          <p class="text-slate-300">Notable alumni: FIN Robotics, Exploride, Asimov Robotics, Sastra Robotics</p>
        </div>

        <figure class="my-10 -mx-4 md:mx-0">
          <img
            src="/images/story/sv-collage.jpg"
            alt="Early Startup Village campus"
            class="w-full aspect-video rounded-xl border border-slate-200 object-cover"
          />
          <figcaption class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-3 px-4 md:px-0 italic">
            Early days at Startup Village — hundreds of young founders, energy, momentum
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </section>

      <!-- The Crack in the Foundation -->
      <section id="the-crack">
        <div class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">2012-2013</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">The Crack in the Foundation</h2>

        <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8">The uncomfortable truth: It was working... but it couldn't scale.</p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-green-900 mb-4">What We Built ✓</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-green-800">
              <li>→ A thriving community</li>
              <li>→ Real outcomes</li>
              <li>→ Mission-driven culture</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-red-900 mb-4">What We Didn't Build ✗</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-red-800">
              <li>→ System that worked without heroic individuals</li>
              <li>→ Predictable, repeatable processes</li>
              <li>→ Product that scaled beyond physical presence</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-slate-900 rounded-r-lg p-8">
          <p class="text-lg italic text-slate-800">
            "We were helping people. But whether we were building something that could actually scale—that was a different question entirely."
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-xl p-6">
          <p class="font-bold mb-2">The Decision (2015)</p>
          <p>Student startups only. Digital-first. Build a real platform.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Silicon Valley Trip -->
      <section id="silicon-valley">
        <div class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">2017</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">The Silicon Valley Trip That Changed Everything</h2>

        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 mb-6">
          <strong>June 2017:</strong> Took a cohort to Silicon Valley — Google Mountain View, Facebook HQ, mentors from top companies
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
          <img
            src="/images/story/google-mountainview.jpg"
            alt="At Google Mountain View"
            class="w-full aspect-[4/3] rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-cover"
          />
          <img
            src="/images/story/facebook-hq.jpg"
            alt="At Facebook HQ"
            class="w-full aspect-[4/3] rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-cover"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-xl p-8 mb-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">The Insight</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-300">
            The Valley wasn't producing great founders because of incubators. It was producing them <strong class="text-white">because the education system was building people who could actually make things.</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300 mt-4">Skills came first. Everything else followed.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-600 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">November 2017: We wrote "SV.CO Chapter 2"</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">December 2017: Communicated to all users</p>
          <p class="text-blue-800">"We're now Internet Product School. The startup narrative is over."</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Pupilfirst Emerges -->
      <section id="pupilfirst">
        <div class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">2018-2021</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Pupilfirst: The Platform Emerges</h2>

        <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <p class="font-bold text-purple-900 mb-2">The Realization (Nov-Dec 2018)</p>
          <p class="text-purple-800">The platform we'd built was comparable to Teachable.com (valued $100M+). We could separate brand from framework → turn it into SaaS.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-purple-700 mt-4"><strong>December 5, 2018:</strong> pupilfirst.com domain registered</p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">What We Built</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mt-0.5">→</span>
              <span>School administration interface</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mt-0.5">→</span>
              <span>Rich curriculum editor (like Medium/Gutenberg)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mt-0.5">→</span>
              <span>Cohort management at scale</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mt-0.5">→</span>
              <span>Submission tracking & feedback systems</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mt-0.5">→</span>
              <span>Complete LMS infrastructure</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mt-0.5">→</span>
              <span>University deployments</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-600 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-6">
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-green-900 mb-2">June 27, 2019: Major Milestone</p>
          <p class="text-green-800">316 commits merged in one day. Student dashboard fully replaced. New curriculum interface live.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">2020: Open-Sourced Everything</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">Full platform. All features. Universities could self-host.</p>
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Result: Gained trust instead of losing customers. Universities wanted to partner, not just purchase.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- RealWorldReady -->
      <section id="realworldready">
        <div class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">2022-2024</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">RealWorldReady: Where Everything Came Together</h2>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <p class="font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">January 2022: Partnered with Dr. Aruna Kesavan</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-800">Former Harvard lecturer · Astrophysicist · 7+ years teaching STEM</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-800 mt-2">Launched HowToCBC → Rebranded to <strong>The Second Design</strong> (March 2024)</p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-6">The Program: RealWorldReady</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 mb-6">Not about startups. Not about developer skills. About <strong>agency.</strong> Teaching students how to create opportunities instead of waiting for them.</p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">The Approach</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <li>→ Practice-heavy (80% doing, 20% consuming)</li>
              <li>→ Students ship work, not just listen</li>
              <li>→ Systems thinking for careers</li>
              <li>→ Real transformation through iteration</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-green-900 mb-3">The Outcomes</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-green-800">
              <li>→ 63% rated sessions 10/10</li>
              <li>→ 1,500+ learners</li>
              <li>→ 30+ sessions developed</li>
              <li>→ Clients: McDonald's, IMG Academy, Glovo</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-xl p-8">
          <p class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">The Gap</p>
          <p class="text-slate-300">Pedagogy was tested. Outcomes were proven. But to scale to millions — we needed infrastructure.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Why EduMyna -->
      <section id="why-edumyna">
        <div class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">Now</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Why EduMyna Exists</h2>

        <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8">After 12 years, here's what I know works:</p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-5">
            <span class="text-green-600 text-2xl mt-1">✓</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-green-900">The infrastructure exists</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-green-800">Pupilfirst LMS — proven, university-deployed, open-source-able</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-5">
            <span class="text-green-600 text-2xl mt-1">✓</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-green-900">The pedagogy is tested</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-green-800">RealWorldReady outcomes show what works</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-5">
            <span class="text-green-600 text-2xl mt-1">✓</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-green-900">The partnerships are proven</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-green-800">Facebook, Apple, Freshworks, 4 state governments</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-5">
            <span class="text-green-600 text-2xl mt-1">✓</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-green-900">The mission is unchanged</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-green-800">Help others enable themselves. Same goal since 2009.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-purple-600 text-white rounded-xl p-10 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">EduMyna = The integration of all these learnings</p>
          <p class="text-xl text-blue-100">Infrastructure + Pedagogy + Partnerships → Scale to millions</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- The Team Vision -->
      <section id="team-vision">
        <div class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">Join Us</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Who We're Looking For</h2>

        <div class="space-y-6 mb-12">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 bg-blue-50 pl-6 py-5 rounded-r-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-3">Developers</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-blue-800">
              <li>→ Believe education can be better</li>
              <li>→ Want to build infrastructure that scales to millions</li>
              <li>→ Care about open-source and ownership</li>
              <li>→ Rails + React/ReasonML experience (or willingness to learn)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-green-600 bg-green-50 pl-6 py-5 rounded-r-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-900 mb-3">Educators / Program Designers</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-green-800">
              <li>→ Understand practice beats content</li>
              <li>→ Can design transformative learning experiences</li>
              <li>→ Want to work at university scale, not just cohort scale</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 bg-purple-50 pl-6 py-5 rounded-r-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-3">Partners (like TinkerHub)</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-purple-800">
              <li>→ Distribution networks that bring students</li>
              <li>→ Mission-aligned nonprofits and communities</li>
              <li>→ University partnerships</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-orange-600 bg-orange-50 pl-6 py-5 rounded-r-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-900 mb-3">Operators</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-orange-800">
              <li>→ Can navigate policy and partnerships</li>
              <li>→ Understand stakeholder alignment</li>
              <li>→ Want to change systems, not just serve users</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Culture</h3>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-slate-300">
            <p>→ Learn in public</p>
            <p>→ Ship fast, iterate faster</p>
            <p>→ Mission-driven, sustainably funded</p>
            <p>→ Section 8 structure (social mission + revenue)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- What We're Not -->
      <section id="what-were-not">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">What We're NOT</h2>

        <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-red-600 text-2xl">×</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-red-900">Not a VC-funded startup</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-red-800">We're Section 8 (nonprofit with revenue). Building for sustainability, not exits.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-red-600 text-2xl">×</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-red-900">Not another certificate mill</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-red-800">We care about capability, not certificates. Practice-heavy programs, real outcomes.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-red-600 text-2xl">×</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-red-900">Not proprietary platform vendors</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-red-800">We're open-source by default. Universities own their infrastructure.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-red-600 text-2xl">×</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-red-900">Not trying to "disrupt" educators</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-red-800">We're giving educators the operational infrastructure to do their work at scale.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- The Journey By Numbers -->
      <section id="by-numbers">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">The Journey So Far — By The Numbers</h2>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-600 mb-3">Startup Village (2009-2015)</p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
              <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">500</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">Startups</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">3,139</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">Jobs</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">₹45Cr</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">Raised</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-600 mb-3">Partnerships (2017-2021)</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-700">Facebook, Apple, Freshworks · 4 state governments · Multiple universities (Manipal, Sastra, GTU, GLS)</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-600 mb-3">The Second Design (2022-2024)</p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
              <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">1,500+</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">Learners</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">63%</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">Rated 10/10</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">100+</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">Sessions</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 text-white rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold">12 years of proof points. Now scaling to millions.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Why Join Now -->
      <section id="why-now">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Why Join Now?</h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-green-900 mb-3">The Timing Is Right</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-green-800">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-green-600">✓</span>
                <span>Infrastructure is ready (don't need to build LMS from scratch)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-green-600">✓</span>
                <span>Pedagogy is tested (RealWorldReady outcomes prove the approach)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-green-600">✓</span>
                <span>Partnerships are warm (universities, corporates, governments engaged)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-green-600">✓</span>
                <span>Structure is clear (Section 8 = mission + sustainability)</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-900 mb-3">What You Get</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-blue-800">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-blue-600">→</span>
                <span>Ground floor of something that can reach millions</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-blue-600">→</span>
                <span>Work on open-source infrastructure</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-blue-600">→</span>
                <span>Mission-aligned culture (not exit-driven)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-blue-600">→</span>
                <span>Learn from 12 years of real operations</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-xl p-10 text-center">
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Chance to fix a broken system</p>
